Sequence Information.Peptide Name: Esculentin-1AA1 (natural AMPs; frog, amphibians, animals; XXU; 1S=S, UCSS1a)

Literature Information.Author: Wang Y, Zhang Y, Lee WH, Yang X, Zhang Y.2015
